items.sentence: Tom doesn\'t earn enough money to support a family.
Tom doesn\'t have many photos of himself as a baby.
Many schools are closed today because of the storm.
My cat likes it when I scratch her behind the ears.
My cousin has a large collection of action figures.
My dog is blind, but he loves to go out for a walk.
My mother is the first one to get up every morning.
The doctors told Tom that Mary would never recover.
There\'s something I\'d like you to take a look at.
I don\'t worry about those kinds of things anymore.
